Devops is a process
Devops is a method

lifecycle of devops is 
plan code build test release deply operate moniotor 

Devops means implementing automation in each and every stage

stages in DEVOPS
1) VERSION CONTROL SYSTEM 
	in this we are maitaining different versions of codes
2) continuous integration
	in this developers regularly merge their code to the central repo
	build and test of code is going on 
	uild and run are going on
	build test integration

3) CONTINUOUS DELIVERY
	Deployment the build app  test server
4) Deployment the test app on the production server for release

Devops is a methodology which allows one team to maintain life cycle of an application like testing,development,deployment,releases
by usimg devops methos we can achieve a software in reliable quality efficient
